          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Medicaid Substance Use Disorder Treatment via Telehealth Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services to develop guidance for states on how to obtain federal reimbursement under Medicaid for substance use disorder telehealth services, including services provided in school-based health centers. </p>]]></text>
